{"tid":2385258,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(小區「清零」?) 林鄭：北角「受限檢測」有實際需要，既可達到小區「清零」、切斷傳播鏈，也可令區內居民安心","createTime":"2021-01-29T02:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T05:58:45.000Z","uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9758b0181c79ec2c31ac4abdd286e40241624262","tid":2385258,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"繼佐敦和油麻地碧街後，政府昨晚在北角錦屏街東發大廈進行另一次「限制與檢測宣告」行動，要求居民留在其處所並按政府安排接受強制檢測，直至區內所有人完成檢測方可離開。「行動」基本上做到保密、聚焦和快速；用了12小時，「限制」令在今早約7時結束。<br />\n<br />\n從效果來看，共有475人接受檢測，未有發現任何確診個案。有人會問，「零」發現是否勞民傷財呢？<br />\n<br />\n今次「受限區域」涵蓋四座(A、B、C、D)超過60年樓齡的舊式樓宇，其中一座於1月18日最先出現首宗確診個案，屬於源頭不明，其後分別於1月20日(有關連)及1月25日(源頭不明)再確診兩宗個案，符合衞生防護中心「一棟樓有兩宗沒有關連個案便須強制檢測」的標準，於1月25日對該大廈C座發出強制檢測公告；及後該處在1月26及27日再出現五宗確診及五宗初步確診個案，經實地調查後，在1月27日安排C座部分可能有垂直傳播風險的住戶入住檢疫中心；為謹慎起見，政府亦向A、B及D座發出強制檢測公告。考慮到個案數字、樓宇狀況、執行能力等因素，我們認為「受限檢測」有其實際需要，既可達到小區「清零」、切斷傳播鏈，也可令區內居民安心。<br />\n<br />\n我昨晚去視察行動進行時，就有居民抱怨他昨天早上已按「強制檢測公告」接受採樣，但由於未收到陰性結果的短訊，須再檢一次。我請他諒解行動的需要，亦感謝他按要求一日兩次接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n抗疫須不斷總結經驗，這次行動說明對某大廈或某小區應進行「強制檢測」或「受限檢測」的決定，應更快、更準、避免訊息混亂，減少對居民帶來不便。<br />\n<br />\n我再次感謝「受限」居民的合作，相關部門同事的努力和私營化驗所承辦商的配合。<br />\n<br />\n#同心抗疫 #<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81e3f95c601e7092788833f5427ac9e15521852","tid":2385258,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"今次真係小區清零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d288d797f2cbe5a10029449aa8742b7ce72ca2f6","tid":2385258,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"冇人確診咪可以除罩囉<br />\n<br />\n都唔明驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a776a647ecee16a56c90721d4be212d5ef742c","tid":2385258,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gggdOBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgggdOBC.jpg&h=4b2e9fa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4deb9202c49739a472f217de2a160b7fb6c33887","tid":2385258,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"大家都驗過冇人中招 戴口罩托咩"},{"pid":"43409c071d6aec9dd3e22011134d82fdd3612ce5","tid":2385258,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1a776a647ecee16a56c90721d4be212d5ef742c","tid":2385258,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gggdOBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgggdOBC.jpg&h=4b2e9fa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cc791ca89b967d4de7d099226878d09d3aeb3b","tid":2385258,"uid":70336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:02:33.000Z","msg":"零咗唔會中？<br />\n全區免疫？"},{"pid":"e558ba7c46418c2aaf705e2426bad3c89d6c4c2d","tid":2385258,"uid":72863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"今日無唔等於聽日無<br />\n唔封關點都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20acdd9a564018305643f80847d90ae1b9911c6","tid":2385258,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"清零？ 你肯定冇假陰性，中招初期一定驗得出？<br />\n外地人咁使咩隔離21日？"},{"pid":"04feac6ccbe62c5eac81aa0672477242da30df2d","tid":2385258,"uid":135890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:03:38.000Z","msg":"無人中：大家安心，有用<br />\n有少少人中：比率高，有用<br />\n勁多人中：揾到大量感染者，有用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cba7eb99c25847545358194032c726ffe263b03","tid":2385258,"uid":62828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"小你老母區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb0c5bd6201adf5dbb36b26ff166f93f4c37f6d","tid":2385258,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">喂有件姓梁嘅object話走撚曬喎</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e68c0fad4bf4973a41265a8e89259f7eb23cd3c7","tid":2385258,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"梁子超：圍封行動未能及早介入會讓流動人口四散<br />\n<br />\n北角東發大廈被列為受限區域的強制檢測行動結束。呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超表示，大廈的660戶中有190戶並無回應，代表不少人已搬走。他認為，如果要處理流動性高的地點，需要及早介入。梁子超於本台節目《千禧年代》表示，圍封行動並無問題，但未能及早介入，會讓流動人口四散，就會像今次一樣未能找出確診人士。他認為當有相連單位有確診個案等高危因素就應考慮採取措施，認為當局應再檢討用甚麼方法才最有效。被問到疫苗問題，梁子超認為，無論任何疫苗，最重要是藥廠能提供所有數據，包括是否能及時提供及數據來源，再由專家參考。<br />\n<br />\n2021-01-29 10:11:28<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e0dafca9054acfaf1ea3fcffdaf745b173b3b9","tid":2385258,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"又可以影相交功課， 有靚靚畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d66941c52a6a37091b3